{"id":308,"parent_id":302,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":308,"title":"1 Kings 6","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Kgs.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 6"],[".studySummary",["i","Solomon builds the temple—The Lord promises to dwell among the Israelites if they are obedient—The ornaments of the temple are described."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.1","order":"02.12.006.24323"},["b","1"],"And it came to pass in the four hundred and eightieth year after the children of Israel were come out of the land of Egypt, in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"fourth"],"year of Solomon’s reign over Israel, in the month Zif, which",["i","is"],"the second month, that he began to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"build"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"house"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.2","order":"02.12.006.24324"},["b","2"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"house"],"which king",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"Solomon"],"built for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", the length thereof",["i","was"],"threescore cubits, and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"breadth"],"thereof twenty",["i","cubits,"],"and the height thereof thirty cubits."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.3","order":"02.12.006.24325"},["b","3"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"porch"],"before the temple of the house, twenty cubits",["i","was"],"the length thereof, according to the breadth of the house;",["i","and"],"ten cubits",["i","was"],"the breadth thereof before the house."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.4","order":"02.12.006.24326"},["b","4"],"And for the house he made",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"windows of narrow lights"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.5","order":"02.12.006.24327"},["b","5"],"¶And against the wall of the house he built",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"chambers"],"round about,",["i","against"],"the walls of the house round about,",["i","both"],"of the temple and of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"oracle"],": and he made chambers round about:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.6","order":"02.12.006.24328"},["b","6"],"The nethermost chamber",["i","was"],"five cubits broad, and the middle",["i","was"],"six cubits broad, and the third",["i","was"],"seven cubits broad: for without",["i","in the wall"],"of the house he made narrowed rests round about, that",["i","the beams"],"should not be fastened in the walls of the house."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.7","order":"02.12.006.24329"},["b","7"],"And the house, when it was in building, was built of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"stone"],"made ready before it was brought thither: so that there was neither hammer nor axe",["i","nor"],"any tool of iron heard in the house, while it was in building."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.8","order":"02.12.006.24330"},["b","8"],"The door for the middle chamber",["i","was"],"in the right side of the house: and they went up with winding stairs into the middle",["i","chamber,"],"and out of the middle into the third."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.9","order":"02.12.006.24331"},["b","9"],"So he built the house, and finished it; and covered the house with beams and boards of cedar."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.10","order":"02.12.006.24332"},["b","10"],"And",["i","then"],"he built chambers against all the house, five cubits high: and they rested on the house with timber of cedar."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.11","order":"02.12.006.24333"},["b","11"],"¶And the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came to Solomon, saying,"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.12","order":"02.12.006.24334"},["b","12"],["i","Concerning"],"this house which thou art in building, if thou wilt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"walk"],"in my statutes, and execute my judgments, and keep all my commandments to walk in them; then will I perform my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"word"],"with thee, which I spake unto David thy father:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.13","order":"02.12.006.24335"},["b","13"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"dwell"],"among the children of Israel, and will not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"forsake"],"my people Israel."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.14","order":"02.12.006.24336"},["b","14"],"So Solomon built the house, and finished it."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.15","order":"02.12.006.24337"},["b","15"],"And he built the walls of the house within with boards of cedar, both the floor of the house, and the walls of the ceiling:",["i","and"],"he covered",["i","them"],"on the inside with wood, and covered the floor of the house with planks of fir."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.16","order":"02.12.006.24338"},["b","16"],"And he built twenty cubits on the sides of the house, both the floor and the walls with boards of cedar: he even built",["i","them"],"for it within,",["i","even"],"for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"oracle"],",",["i","even"],"for the most",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"holy",["i","place"]],["i","."]],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.17","order":"02.12.006.24339"},["b","17"],"And the house, that",["i","is,"],"the temple before it, was forty cubits",["i","long."]],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.18","order":"02.12.006.24340"},["b","18"],"And the cedar of the house within",["i","was"],"carved with knops and open flowers: all",["i","was"],"cedar; there was no stone seen."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.19","order":"02.12.006.24341"},["b","19"],"And the oracle he prepared in the house within, to set there the ark of the covenant of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.20","order":"02.12.006.24342"},["b","20"],"And the oracle in the forepart",["i","was"],"twenty cubits in length, and twenty cubits in breadth, and twenty cubits in the height thereof: and he overlaid it with pure gold; and",["i","so"],"covered the altar",["i","which was of"],"cedar."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.21","order":"02.12.006.24343"},["b","21"],"So Solomon overlaid the house within with pure",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"gold"],": and he made a partition by the chains of gold before the oracle; and he overlaid it with gold."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.22","order":"02.12.006.24344"},["b","22"],"And the whole house he overlaid with gold, until he had finished all the house: also the whole",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"altar"],"that",["i","was"],"by the oracle he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"overlaid"],"with gold."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.23","order":"02.12.006.24345"},["b","23"],"¶And within the oracle he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"made"],"two",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"cherubims"],["i","of"],"olive tree,",["i","each"],"ten cubits high."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.24","order":"02.12.006.24346"},["b","24"],"And five cubits",["i","was"],"the one wing of the cherub, and five cubits the other wing of the cherub: from the uttermost part of the one wing unto the uttermost part of the other",["i","were"],"ten cubits."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.25","order":"02.12.006.24347"},["b","25"],"And the other cherub",["i","was"],"ten cubits: both the cherubims",["i","were"],"of one measure and one size."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.26","order":"02.12.006.24348"},["b","26"],"The height of the one cherub",["i","was"],"ten cubits, and so",["i","was it"],"of the other cherub."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.27","order":"02.12.006.24349"},["b","27"],"And he set the cherubims within the inner house: and they stretched forth the wings of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"cherubims"],", so that the wing of the one touched the",["i","one"],"wall, and the wing of the other cherub touched the other wall; and their wings touched one another in the midst of the house."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.28","order":"02.12.006.24350"},["b","28"],"And he overlaid the cherubims with gold."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.29","order":"02.12.006.24351"},["b","29"],"And he carved all the walls of the house round about with carved figures of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"cherubims"],"and palm trees and open flowers, within and without."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.30","order":"02.12.006.24352"},["b","30"],"And the floor of the house he overlaid with gold, within and without."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.31","order":"02.12.006.24353"},["b","31"],"¶And for the entering of the oracle he made",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"doors"],["i","of"],"olive tree: the lintel",["i","and"],"side posts",["i","were"],"a fifth part",["i","of the wall."]],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.32","order":"02.12.006.24354"},["b","32"],"The two doors also",["i","were of"],"olive tree; and he carved upon them carvings of cherubims and palm trees and open flowers, and overlaid",["i","them"],"with gold, and spread gold upon the cherubims, and upon the palm trees."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.33","order":"02.12.006.24355"},["b","33"],"So also made he for the door of the temple posts",["i","of"],"olive tree, a fourth part",["i","of the wall."]],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.34","order":"02.12.006.24356"},["b","34"],"And the two doors",["i","were of"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"fir tree"],": the two leaves of the one door",["i","were"],"folding, and the two leaves of the other door",["i","were"],"folding."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.35","order":"02.12.006.24357"},["b","35"],"And he carved",["i","thereon"],"cherubims and palm trees and open flowers: and covered",["i","them"],"with gold fitted upon the carved work."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.36","order":"02.12.006.24358"},["b","36"],"¶And he built the inner",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"court"],"with three rows of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_36b"},"hewed"],"stone, and a row of cedar beams."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.37","order":"02.12.006.24359"},["b","37"],"¶In the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"fourth"],"year was the foundation of the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"laid, in the month Zif:"],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.38","order":"02.12.006.24360"},["b","38"],"And in the eleventh year, in the month Bul, which",["i","is"],"the eighth month, was the house finished throughout all the parts thereof, and according to all the fashion of it. So was he seven years in building it."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.1a","order":"02.12.006.24361"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.37"},"1 Kgs. 6:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.1b","order":"02.12.006.24363"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/3.1.1-17"},"2 Chr. 3:1 (1–17)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/skill"},"TG Skill"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.1c","order":"02.12.006.24365"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.119"},"D&C 88:119"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.27.26-27"},"124:27 (26–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.2a","order":"02.12.006.24367"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/3.3.3-4"},"2 Chr. 3:3 (3–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.13"},"D&C 95:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.2b","order":"02.12.006.24369"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/5.16"},"2 Ne. 5:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.2c","order":"02.12.006.24371"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.2"},"Ezek. 41:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.3a","order":"02.12.006.24373"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/8.16"},"Ezek. 8:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.49"},"40:49"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/10.23"},"John 10:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.11"},"Acts 3:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.4a","order":"02.12.006.24375"},["b","4a"],["span.small","OR"],"recessed and latticed windows."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.5a","order":"02.12.006.24377"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.6.5-9,11"},"Ezek. 41:6 (5–9, 11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.5b","order":"02.12.006.24379"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/7.49"},"1 Kgs. 7:49"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.8.6,8"},"8:8 (6, 8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.39"},"D&C 124:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.7a","order":"02.12.006.24381"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.17"},"1 Kgs. 5:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.12a","order":"02.12.006.24383"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/9.4"},"1 Kgs. 9:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.55"},"D&C 124:55"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.12b","order":"02.12.006.24385"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.13"},"2 Sam. 7:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.10"},"1 Chr. 22:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.13a","order":"02.12.006.24387"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/25.8"},"Ex. 25:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.24,27"},"D&C 124:24, 27"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.13b","order":"02.12.006.24389"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/31.6.6,8"},"Deut. 31:6 (6, 8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.5"},"Josh. 1:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/13.5"},"Heb. 13:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.16a","order":"02.12.006.24391"},["b","16a"],["span.small","IE"],"innermost room of the temple of Solomon; the Holy of Holies."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.16b","order":"02.12.006.24393"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/26.33"},"Ex. 26:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/7.50"},"1 Kgs. 7:50"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.6"},"8:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/3.8"},"2 Chr. 3:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.4.1-4"},"Ezek. 41:4 (1–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.39"},"D&C 124:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.21a","order":"02.12.006.24395"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/5.15"},"2 Ne. 5:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.26.26-27"},"D&C 124:26 (26–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.22a","order":"02.12.006.24397"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/30.1"},"Ex. 30:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.22b","order":"02.12.006.24399"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/30.3"},"Ex. 30:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.23a","order":"02.12.006.24401"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/art"},"TG Art"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.23b","order":"02.12.006.24403"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cherubim"},"TG Cherubim"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.27a","order":"02.12.006.24405"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.3.2-3"},"Alma 42:3 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.29a","order":"02.12.006.24407"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/7.36"},"1 Kgs. 7:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.18"},"Ezek. 41:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.31a","order":"02.12.006.24409"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.23"},"Ezek. 41:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.34a","order":"02.12.006.24411"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.8"},"1 Kgs. 5:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"36a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.36a","order":"02.12.006.24413"},["b","36a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.5"},"2 Kgs. 21:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/8.16"},"Ezek. 8:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.4.4-5"},"D&C 94:4 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"36b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.36b","order":"02.12.006.24415"},["b","36b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/7.11"},"1 Kgs. 7:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.37a","order":"02.12.006.24417"},["b","37a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.1"},"1 Kgs. 6:1"],"."]]}
